        <h1>What is Food Panda</h1>
        <p>Foodpanda is a mobile app that lets you order food from your favorite restaurants and have it delivered right to your doorstep. It is a convenient and affordable way to enjoy delicious meals without having to leave your home. The app is free to use and offers a wide variety of restaurants to choose from, so you're sure to find something you'll love.</p>

        <h2 id="Inst">Installation Guide!</h2>
        <p>**Steps to use Food Panda:**</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Download and install the Food Panda app on your mobile phone.<br> Please click "Get it On Google Play" if you're an Android user, otherwise <br> click "Download on the Apple Store".</li>
            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.global.foodpanda.android&hl=en&gl=US"><img src="/images/For-Logos/to_google_play_store.png" width="180" height="70"></a>
            <a href="https://apps.apple.com/sg/app/foodpanda-food-groceries/id758103884"><img src="/images/For-Logos/to_apple_store.png" width="180" height="60"></a>
            <p></p>
        </ol>

        <h2 id = "req">Requirements</h2>
        <p>Make sure you have your Food Panda app downloaded</p>
        <img src = "/images/Food Panda/Home Page.jpg" width = "300px"><br><br>

        <h2 id = "Ordering">Ordering Meals</h2>
        <p>Press on the Food delivery input box</p>
        <img src = "/images/Food Panda/Ordering/HomePage.jpg" width = "300px"><br><br>

        <p>Press on search bar to find the restaurant you want to order from</p>
        <img src = "/images/Food Panda/Ordering/Step2.jpg" width = "300px"><br><br>

        <p>After locating the restaurant you want, locate the meal you want ordered to your house</p>
        <img src = "/images/Food Panda/Ordering/Step3.jpg" width = "300px"><br><br>

        <p>Customize your meal according to your preference and press on "Add to cart" once completed</p>
        <img src = "/images/Food Panda/Ordering/Step4.jpg" width = "300px"><br><br>

        <p>If you don't want to order anything else, you can press on view your cart to confirm your order!!!</p>
        <img src = "/images/Food Panda/Ordering/FinalStep.jpg" width = "300px"><br><br>
